Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did Suna say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:11.74,Phone,Sign 0005,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}From: Yukika-chan \N\NYamato-san, \NThank you for your help yesterday. Thanks to you \Nand Takeo-kun, I was able to invite Sunakawa-kun \Nto the zoo. Thank you for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:05.23,Message Body - Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the city, trying to buy some clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.23,Message Body - Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm having trouble picking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.08,Message Body - Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If you happen to be free,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.74,Message Body - Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,would it be possible for you to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan, sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're going on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'd want to get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:18.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:21.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what kind of clothes to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You want him to think you look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.12,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,With any luck, I hope he'll like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:29.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no idea what kind \Nof clothes I should wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,so that he'll like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try asking Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.26,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0037,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of clothes does Sunakawa-kun like girls to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:39.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, what kind of clothes do you like on girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:40.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:42.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:41.89,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0042,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Maybe this fits the zoo theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:42.81,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0042,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Oh come on,      Maybe this fits the zoo theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,anything normal is fine, if it suits the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Normal clothes that suit Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:47.52,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0048,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Wow these shoes have \Nreally high heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.36,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0048,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}I couldn't...                              Wow these shoes have \Nreally high heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Traditional Japanese clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, they can be Western clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:51.15,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.36,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,Cute                                                            But expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking clothes that suit anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.11,Phone,Sign 0056,0000,0000,0000,,Subject:     Re: Sunakawa-kun \N\NHe says school uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:58.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wear my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he means wear anything, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.95,SFX-GrayWhite,Sign 0101,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan's dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.76,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She froze when she saw Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Suna's good-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:48.27,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing him up close, she must be feeling \Noverwhelmed and paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.77,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 02429,0000,0000,0000,,Talk!                                           Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But she has to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of asking him out \Nif you won't talk, Yukika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:03:00.53,SignA,Sign 0258,0000,0000,0000,,Busai Zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.53,Title1,Sign 0303,0000,0000,0000,,The Letter to Me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I picked the zoo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,During an elementary school field trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:12.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun asked why \Nwe call the giraffe "kirin."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:16.30,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,No one knew the answer, so that ended it then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,it was because it's named after \Na mythical beast in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I just didn't have the courage to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:33.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to make some \Ngood memories at the zoo today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can you take our picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So tell that to Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.94,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0338,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!!                            Good luck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When I look back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I think having Sunakawa-kun save \Nme from the ball in dodgeball
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,was my prime time moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Price time? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:48.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Prime time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.35,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It means the best time of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.83,SFX-Red,Sign 0351,0000,0000,0000,,The Best Time of Your Life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That happened way too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. Suna isn't scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just follow the route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.84,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Too Close
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:13.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:18.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:19.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.77,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A petting zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:21.90,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.15,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.53,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Petting Zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:29.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, you remind me of a cute critter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:35.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm small, but maybe I'm a carnivore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one reminds me of Yukika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think, I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took it the wrong way at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's really impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla reminds me of you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.24,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0505,0000,0000,0000,,You don't always hold back, huh?                     {\c&H0D0B04&}Does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but I wouldn't stand \Na chance against him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}is{\i0} strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he would be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A downpour!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just to get out of the rain for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.85,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If it's with Sunakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So tell Suna that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan, you won't make any \Nmemories with him this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you look like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm thinking you look like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.78,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, I'm starting to really like gorillas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.00,SFX - WhiteBlack,Sign 0555,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}I love her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.28,SignA,Sign 0556,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3D8766&}Postcards
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:04.55,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There isn't a postcard of \Nthe bird you really liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem that popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there wouldn't be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.44,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0620,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.32,Default,YTYu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.84,Default - italics,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a trivia competition \Nin front of Monkey Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.02,Default - italics,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,We encourage everyone to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:34.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.96,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now begin the trivia competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.72,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like to join, please form pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.72,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Can the pairs join hands, so that \Nwe know how many there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.35,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0655,0000,0000,0000,,Petrified
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I should have paired up with Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.94,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-two pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.53,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,You can let go of each other's hand now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.56,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.79,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the first question, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.79,SFX-BlackWhite,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Whoa, it's starting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.83,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,The giraffe's tongue is purple
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.29,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,in order to absorb UV rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.85,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,True or false? Move to circle or X.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's false.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.55,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's false!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.72,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is "false"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.93,Sunakawa,Sign 0736,0000,0000,0000,,Q2: Elephants have four teeth. \NTrue or False?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.06,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the second question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.81,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,The third question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.43,Sunakawa,Sign 0738,0000,0000,0000,,Q3: Rhinoceros horns are shed and regrown every year. \NTrue or False?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's false!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.32,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.93,Sunakawa,Sign 0739,0000,0000,0000,,Q4: The Japanese serow is not in the same family as the deer. \NTrue or False?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:39.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:40.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,False!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:44.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.28,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Now we only have two pairs, \Nso here is the final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.78,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,The first pair to answer correctly will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.09,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Which zebra is at this zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.09,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Zebra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.79,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the mountain zebra, the plains \Nzebra, or the Grévy's zebra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the plains zebra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.04,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.02,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Amami-san, you know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.30,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.99,Default,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the prize, coasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:12.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're both amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.59,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was Amami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I like reading books, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.69,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything to read lying around, \NI find myself reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You used to read a lot in kindergarten, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Sunakawa-kun! You're always reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go walk Yamato home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:35.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:39.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it was fun. I hadn't been for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You talked to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.30,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0852,0000,0000,0000,,I was all nervous for you, too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:54.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.74,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you summoned the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:06.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Today was the happiest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Slime time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.19,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Prime time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:16.73,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I talked about small things with \NSunakawa-kun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It was really nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:24.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but Sunakawa-kun nodded and laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:31.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to be that way with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.47,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.47,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 0938,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!            Good luck at school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.92,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nodding and listening to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.10,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,smiling at what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:50.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's right... That might be the happiest thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.95,EyecatchB,Sign 1003,0000,0000,0000,,First
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.70,EyecatchB,Sign 1005,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Love
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.95,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.09,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.96,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.50,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,For real? Why's she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't a spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.09,SFX-GrayWhite,Sign 1014,0000,0000,0000,,Rooftop Entry Forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun's so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He came to the zoo because he's kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.42,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He smiled because he's kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:35.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Sunakawa-kun dislikes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:39.31,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't mean he likes me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He's just being kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.73,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't that I don't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.55,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't want to, I wouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,979)}When I looked at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I felt something off. \NSo that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't not like her, but he \Ndoesn't like her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:11:01.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,At night and stuff, I wonder what \NSunakawa-kun might be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:05.25,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we might randomly \Nrun into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.14,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:16.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Sunakawa-kun \Nthinks that way about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.28,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell these things, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.01,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,How we feel about each other is so different
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell Sunakawa-kun that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have told him how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.14,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not disliking someone is different \Nthan liking someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:00.71,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense Yukika-chan anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:10.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I got a text message from Yukika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.87,Phone,Sign 1212,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Thank you for everything. \NI'll never forget how you helped me \Npick out clothes. Goodbye. \NI don't think we'll be seeing each other again. \NMay you be happy with Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I replied to her text, but she hasn't written back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even answer my calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She said that it was getting painful, \Nhow kind Suna was to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:31.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That she was heartbroken because they \Nfelt so differently about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:38.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:42.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop by the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.32,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much closure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:03.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad that it just faded out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:09.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan was saying that she \Nwished she'd never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you agree, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If she thought about it more,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,she'd remember there were some fun times, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:20.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.78,Default - flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.51,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,The zoo yesterday was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.54,Phone,Sign 1336,0000,0000,0000,,Delete Photo? \NDelete    Cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:39.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say sad things like you wish \Nyou'd never said anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:50.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:51.50,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1351,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, I found Yukika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's headed for the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:03.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to disappear from \Nall of our lives, Yukika—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.39,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna might only be nice to you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but aren't you just getting started?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.87,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.29,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,How can I keep talking to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,when I know he doesn't have feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:27.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not tough like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But, Yukika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:33.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the letter you left for Suna with \Nhis chocolate, back in kindergarten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was really impressed when I saw the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "This must be how it is \Nwhen someone really likes you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:51.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's why even Suna still remembers the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's nice to just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's too sad to have things end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, where's Yukika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:14.10,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in front of the ladies' room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.24,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a peeping tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.35,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We're discussing an important issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.57,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, next time, try not to act so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:33.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So my letter was impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:42.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,it would be sad if I never spoke \Nto Sunakawa-kun again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.63,Phone,Sign 1549,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call \NSunakawa-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sunakawa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:52.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's me, Sunakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:02.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Amami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.31,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.31,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.35,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He says he wants to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go meet with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan, we'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Sunakawa-kun's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:34.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but Suna is kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for asking you to come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.69,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to thank you for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.96,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1703,0000,0000,0000,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:18.47,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being so nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:29.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you at school, \Ncan we still talk like friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:33.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.71,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.87,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He has such good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.85,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly the kind of thing I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He said this was for all ten years \Nof giving him chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.09,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He apologized to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.18,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:11.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to Takeo-kun and Yamato-san \Nuntil late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.44,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Picking clothes with Yamato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Going home with Sunakawa-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,though I couldn't talk to him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the zoo with Sunakawa-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,though I couldn't talk to him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have a lot of happy memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.69,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,His world and mine overlapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.47,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I told him how I felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.03,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.48,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be like you, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He loves you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:03.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When he's with you, \NSunakawa-kun laughs out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:09.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I like how he laughs when he's with you the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:13.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just jump into a river like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write letters like you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, too, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.39,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Though in a completely different way from \Nhow I like Sunakawa-kun, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to tell Suna everything you wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:39.78,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1933,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(948,1811)}I don't need anything in return, so please like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I told him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I've been telling him for the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,so I want him to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.78,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.20,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that was the \Nmost difficult thing to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.47,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.42,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If someone you like returns the feeling, \Nyou don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I want Sunakawa-kun to date a really nice girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:20:01.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,who's really kind and cute, and likes \NSunakawa-kun even more than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:06.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I want Sunakawa-kun to like someone \Nand to date that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk home with Yukika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You had curry today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When Amami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:48.12,Default - flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took it the wrong way at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When she apologized to you at the zoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.36,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2059,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:06.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, do you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's what Yukika-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone not like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find someone you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm having a great enough time as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, you end up in tears \Nafter liking someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:35.98,SignA,Sign 2119,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H257D3A&\fad(906,1)}The bird's name is the "Bali myna." \N— Amami Yukika
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:34.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But liking someone is still a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Title2,Sign 2248,0000,0000,0000,,My Spring Break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.31,Default - margin,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Spring Break.
